## Accessibility

- [ ] All text meets WCAG AA contrast at its smallest used size.
- [ ] Focus states are visible without relying on color alone.
- [ ] Tap targets ≥ 44×44 px (mobile) or ≥ 24×24 px keyboard-focusable area (web).
- [ ] Color is not the only signal for state (use icon + color, not color alone).

